This project is a personal portfolio work designed to demonstrate front-end 
development skills with React 19, Tailwind CSS, and Modern UI/UX principles.

You are free to:
1. View the code for educational purposes.
2. Clone or fork the repository to review the architecture on your local machine.
3. Use parts of the code for your own personal learning projects.

You may NOT:
1. Use this project (or substantial parts of it) for commercial purposes.
2. Sell this template or distribute it as a paid product.
3. Remove the original author's (Yunusisback) credits from the code.

This software is provided "as is", without warranty of any kind.

